name: Lushtemples — Mint
description:
Special edition HEN500K
—
The Lushtemples are a series of generative drawings that explore the graphic density of nature untamed ; the works remain aware of the un-natural process of re-creating nature, by introducing hints of artificiality such as elements of architecture or destructive digital modifiers. 

Code in Javascript.
